c: 60
v: 11
t: "Nihagira umwe mu bagore banyu ubacika agasanga abahakanyi (ntibabasubize inkwano mwabatanzeho), hanyuma habaho kurwana na bo mukabatsinda (mukagira iminyago mubakuraho), mujye muha abo abagore babo bagiye (bakaza babasanga) ibingana n’ibyo bari barabatanzeho (inkwano). Kandi mugandukire Allah We mwemera"